  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What is Vue Router?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Vue Router is the official routing library for Vue.js used to create navigation between different views in a single-page application (SPA)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Why Use Vue Router?"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Enable SPA navigation**",
        "**Manage routes easily**",
        "**Dynamic component rendering**",
        "**Better user experience without page reload**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Basic Concept"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Instead of loading new pages, Vue Router dynamically updates components based on the URL."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Install Vue Router"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "npm install vue-router"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Basic Setup"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router';\n\nconst routes = [\n  { path: '/', component: Home },\n  { path: '/about', component: About }\n];\n\nconst router = createRouter({\n  history: createWebHistory(),\n  routes\n});"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Router View"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<router-view></router-view>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Navigation Links"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<router-link to=\"/\">Home</router-link>\n<router-link to=\"/about\">About</router-link>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Programmatic Navigation"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "this.$router.push('/about');"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use named routes for clarity**",
        "**Organize routes in separate files**",
        "**Use lazy loading for routes**",
        "**Keep routing logic clean**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Mistakes"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Not defining routes properly**",
        "**Forgetting router-view**",
        "**Using wrong paths**",
        "**Not handling navigation errors**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Vue Router is essential for building modern SPAs, enabling smooth navigation and dynamic component rendering."
    }
